.TH "tsi721_lcread" 9 "tsi721_lcread" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
tsi721_lcread \- read from local SREP config space
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" tsi721_lcread
.BI "(struct rio_mport *mport "  ","
.BI "int index "  ","
.BI "u32 offset "  ","
.BI "int len "  ","
.BI "u32 *data "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "mport" 12
RapidIO master port info
.IP "index" 12
ID of RapdiIO interface
.IP "offset" 12
Offset into configuration space
.IP "len" 12
Length (in bytes) of the maintenance transaction
.IP "data" 12
Value to be read into
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Generates a local SREP space read. Returns 0 on
success or -EINVAL on failure.
